Know Before You Hire"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-muted text-lg leading-relaxed border-l-2 border-teal pl-4","children":"Drone footage looks incredible but there's more to it than pointing a camera at the sky. Here's what to understand before hiring a drone operator for your project."}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"border-t border-white/[0.06] mb-10"}]}],["$","article",null,{"className":"max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 pb-16","children":[[["$","p","0",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["Aerial footage has gone from something only major productions could afford to something available to almost any project. Drones have democratized aerial cinematography, and the Gulf Coast — with its coastlines, waterways, and sprawling landscapes — is one of the most visually compelling places in the country to fly them."]}],["$","p","1",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["But drone videography is more regulated and technically involved than most people realize. Here's what you need to know before you hire a drone operator."]}],["$","h2","2",{"className":"font-display text-2xl tracking-widest text-white mt-10 mb-4","children":"FAA Certification Is Not Optional"}],["$","p","3",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["Any drone operator being paid for commercial work in the United States is required by federal law to hold an FAA Part 107 Remote Pilot Certificate. This isn't a technicality — it's a legal requirement, and flying commercially without it creates liability for both the operator and the client."]}],["$","p","4",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["When hiring a drone operator, always ask for proof of their Part 107 certification. A professional will have it readily available. If someone hesitates or says they don't need it, that's a serious red flag."]}],["$","h2","5",{"className":"font-display text-2xl tracking-widest text-white mt-10 mb-4","children":"Airspace Is Regulated"}],["$","p","6",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["Not everywhere is open to drone flight. Airports, heliports, national parks, military installations, and many urban areas have restricted or controlled airspace that requires advance authorization to fly in."]}],["$","p","7",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["An experienced drone operator will know how to check airspace, file the necessary authorizations, and obtain permits when required. This process can take days or weeks in some cases, so if your project requires drone work in a restricted area, plan ahead."]}],["$","h2","8",{"className":"font-display text-2xl tracking-widest text-white mt-10 mb-4","children":"What Good Drone Footage Actually Looks Like"}],["$","p","9",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["The ability to fly a drone and the ability to capture cinematic aerial footage are two different things. Good drone footage involves:"]}],["$","ul","10",{"className":"list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2","children":[["$","li","0",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed","children":"Intentional, smooth movements that tell a story or establish a location"}],["$","li","1",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed","children":"Proper exposure for the sky and ground simultaneously"}],["$","li","2",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed","children":"Thoughtful framing and composition, not just height"}],["$","li","3",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed","children":"Footage that integrates naturally with the ground-level coverage"}]]}],["$","p","11",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["Ask to see previous aerial work — ideally projects similar to yours. Flying low and fast over a wedding venue requires different skills than slow, sweeping coastal shots for a real estate listing."]}],["$","h2","12",{"className":"font-display text-2xl tracking-widest text-white mt-10 mb-4","children":"Weather and Conditions"}],["$","p","13",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["Drones cannot fly in rain, high winds, or certain low-visibility conditions. Any project that depends on drone footage should have a weather contingency plan. A professional operator will not fly in unsafe conditions, and you should not want them to."]}],["$","h2","14",{"className":"font-display text-2xl tracking-widest text-white mt-10 mb-4","children":"The Gulf Coast Is Spectacular from the Air"}],["$","p","15",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["Few regions in the country offer the visual variety of the Gulf Coast from above — barrier islands, bayous, historic downtowns, working waterfronts, and some of the most beautiful beaches in the country. If your project has any visual storytelling component, aerial footage of this region is almost always worth including."]}],["$","p","16",{"className":"text-white/75 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["Find a certified, experienced operator and give them time to plan the flight properly. The results speak for themselves."]}]],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-teal/10 to-transparent border border-teal/20 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"font-display text-2xl tracking-widest mb-3","children":"Find a Professional on the Gulf Coast"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-muted text-sm mb-6","children":"Browse verified media professionals available for your next project — from Tallahassee to New Orleans."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex gap-4 justify-center flex-wrap","children":[["$","$L2",null,{"href":"/browse","className":"btn-teal font-display tracking-widest px-6 py-2","children":"Browse Pros"}],["$","$L2",null,{"href":"/post-job","className":"btn-outline font-display tracking-widest px-6 py-2","children":"Post a Job"}]]}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"bg-navy2 border-t border-white/[0.06] py-12 px-4","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-6xl mx-auto","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"font-display text-2xl tracking-widest mb-8 text-center","children":"More Guides"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-5","children":[["$","$L2","how-to-prepare-for-a-professional-video-shoot",{"href":"/blog/how-to-prepare-for-a-professional-video-shoot","className":"card p-5 hover:border-teal/40 transition-all duration-200 group","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"font-condensed text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase bg-teal/10 text-teal border border-teal/20 px-2 py-0.5 rounded mb-3 inline-block","children":"Production Tips"}],["$","h3",null,{"className":"font-condensed text-sm tracking-wide text-white group-hover:text-teal transition-colors leading-snug","children":"How to Prepare Your Business for a Professional Video Shoot"}]]}],["$","$L2","what-to-expect-from-professional-audio-engineering",{"href":"/blog/what-to-expect-from-professional-audio-engineering","className":"card p-5 hover:border-teal/40 transition-all duration-200 group","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"font-condensed text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase bg-teal/10 text-teal border border-teal/20 px-2 py-0.5 rounded mb-3 inline-block","children":"Industry Basics"}],["$","h3",null,{"className":"font-condensed text-sm tracking-wide text-white group-hover:text-teal transition-colors leading-snug","children":"What to Expect from a Professional Audio Engineer"}]]}],["$","$L2","social-media-video-what-your-business-needs-to-know",{"href":"/blog/social-media-video-what-your-business-needs-to-know","className":"card p-5 hover:border-teal/40 transition-all duration-200 group","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"font-condensed text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase bg-teal/10 text-teal border border-teal/20 px-2 py